originalText.text: Dr Chuu is amazing—she’s very thorough, explains things deeply, takes her time with you, answers all of your questions, and knows her stuff. And she’s deeply compassionate about her patients and you feel it. She’s just the best. Been my OB for many years now. I feel lucky to have found her!

originalText.text: I personally had an experience with Dr Chuu that left me traumatized. I do not feel like she was sensitive to the issues I had. I had to see her twice a year for two years for the same issue she diagnosed me with and every time I saw her I felt like she forgot about the last time I saw her. After a particularly painful procedure I was left in tears and she promptly left the room. I only went to her because my gyno left Mount Sinai and she was the replacement doctor they recommended. If you have reproductive health issues, stay away.

originalText.text: Hands down the best doctor I’ve ever had. Dr. Chuu saw me throughout my pregnancy as well as delivered my baby less then two weeks ago. She’s a very knowledgeable, up to date professional with amazing bed side manners. It was a real pleasure being her patient and I can’t imagine any other doctor being my gynecologist and obstetrician.
